title: LF OOL Team
body: Hi, i am an ADC player looking for an OOL team, i am currently diamond 5 and my peak is diamond 3. I am able to put in countless hours to improve and already have a personal coach that it helping me with my play. please add me in game "staller" or comment on here if you think you have a team for me. I will be playing to win XD

replies.body: hey dude. im not a owner of a team but was just wondering if you can add me and help me with some things :)
